{"tid":355063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中西區會拒論平反六四　遭覆核","createTime":"2017-08-11T03:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T05:30:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e10ebdea900221bb249e7485174e5f2479b65c7f","tid":355063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20117910&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20117910%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170811&d=z4mDHYM5U6lFCLixjcIXVROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=54f8b071\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20117910%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170811&h=00041959\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20117910&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170811</a><br />\n<br />\n中西區會拒論平反六四　遭覆核<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志林淳軒（右）昨在許智峯陪同下入稟申司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】居於中西區的香港眾志林淳軒不滿中西區區議會主席葉永成，多次拒絕民主黨許智峯提交要求「平反六四」的文件，亦拒絕討論及表決有關動議，昨入稟高等法院申請司法覆核，要求法庭頒令葉的決定屬不合法及不合理。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯六提動議被拒<br />\n<br />\n林表示翻查記錄，過往議會亦曾討論白皮書等政治議題，惟葉卻稱「平反六四」屬政治議題，不應在議會上討論，質疑「建制派想討論嘅就唔係政治問題」。<br />\n陪同林淳軒到法院入稟的許智峯表示，無論上屆及今屆區議會均曾多次提出要討論「平反六四」的相關文件但遭拒，形容葉的做法濫權。許是立法會及中西區區議會雙料議員。<br />\n入稟狀指，許智峯於2014至今年5月，曾6度提出要求討論「平反六四」的動議但都不得要領。林認為區議會作為地區諮詢組織，應討論公眾關注的議題，例如「平反六四」，但葉未有提供合理解釋下便拒絕許的動議。<br />\n案件編號：HCAL507/17<br />\n■記者蘇曉欣"},{"pid":"8b92d7b7870a2d453dd7eaf1a6b8209627824354","tid":355063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170811/large/11la8p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170811%2Flarge%2F11la8p06.jpg&h=872b5373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港眾志林淳軒（右）昨在許智峯陪同下入稟申司法覆核。"},{"pid":"03522df1f75a36d2a49fcc46bbd8d4c34395349f","tid":355063,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:30:12.000Z","msg":"有咩問題，關區議會撚事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}